<div class="container">
    <h3>Getting Started</h3>
    <p>To use this API, you must first start with this base URL <code>http://wattsun-k92aes2xkf.elasticbeanstalk.com/</code>.  The API is a simple resource based programing interface and only requires <strong>GET</strong> HTTP requests. The response body will always be formatted as JSON and will contain a <code>status_code</code> with every response.</p>
    <hr>
